Proposed law authorizes onsite saltwater disposal well operators with an existing permit that
limits the injection pressure to an amount less than those provided by proposed law to apply
to the dept. to have their permits modified to comply with proposed law.
Proposed law specifies that proposed law does not apply to commercial saltwater disposal
wells.
